Nollywood actor, Yul Edochie, has replied those criticising him for marrying a second wife and having a new baby with the new wife, stating that silence is not always the best answer but he would soon speak his mind over the matter. The actor disclosed this on Wednesday while responding to critics in regards to his second marriage to the Nigerian actress, Judy Austin who gave birth to a son for the actor. Edochie wrote, “Silence is good but it’s certainly not always the best answer. -Advertisement- “It has gotten to the point where I’ll speak.” Recall that the actor on Wednesday, April 27, 2022, via his Instagram page announced the existence of his son and his marriage to the mother of the child, declaring the Nigerian actress publicly as his second wife.